\b 3. Delivery\
\

\b0 Practice, practice, practice\
\
Practice in front of an audience (spouse, strangers, friends)\
\
Practice in front of people who have never seen or heard your content before\
\

\b Be relaxed about it
\b0  - if you practice enough, you will internalize it to the point where you can \'93wing it\'94\
\
\

\b Pro Tip: 
\b0 Try to be relaxed, get up and engage with the audience\
\
